OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMinister rejects national  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fmisogyny and racism inquiry
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A national inquiry into institutional  
OL,6, misogyny and racism in the workplace   
OL,7, has been rejected by the government.   
OL,9,FThe inquiry was called for by the      
OL,10,Fauthors of a damning report into London
OL,11,FFire Brigade's workplace culture.      
OL,13,FIt found "dangerous levels of prejudice
OL,14,Fagainst women" while those from        
OL,15,Fminority backgrounds were "frequently  
OL,16,Fthe target of racist abuse".           
OL,18,FNazir Afzal, who led the report, said  
OL,19,Fit was a national issue and called for 
OL,20,Fa wider inquiry.                       
